Documentation for the project is written in reStructuredText__, a plain-text
markup language, and compiled into HTML with Sphinx__. 

__ http://docutils.sourceforge.net/rst.html
__ http://sphinx.pocoo.org

Documentation can be read in three ways:

#. In plain-text form, i.e. by looking at ``.rst`` files
#. Through local HTML documentation: run ``make html`` from the ``docs`` folder.
#. Online at ReadTheDocs.org__

__ http://wehave-weneed.readthedocs.org
